data.description: A patch of 5 Acre paradise located in United Local Schools, surrounded by beautiful countryside and only 5 minutes from Guilford! New metal roof in 2023! This is a spacious 3 bedroom one floor living home with a large living room, large open kitchen with dining area with tons of cabinets and counter space. Master suite offers a full bath and large closet and linen closet. Two additional bedrooms and full bath, convenience of first floor laundry and lots of storage enhance this comfortable floor plan. Newer faucets in the bathrooms as well as backsplashes. Great place to entertain with the private back yard and a covered deck with peaceful views offering 5 acres of endless possibilities - bring chickens, horses or other animals, room for a garden, shooting range and many activities. Can sell furnished at an acceptable offer and all appliances stay!  Lot line pics are not correct, back lot line actually extends further in the back of the property to the bottom of the hill, through the woods and has property markers at the corner.
